# Next.js 15 Conventions

- Use App Router (not Pages Router)
- Server Components by default; add 'use client' only when needed (hooks, events, browser APIs)
- Use `@/` path alias for all imports (maps to `src/`)
- Route handlers use `NextRequest` and return `NextResponse` or use `withApi` wrapper
- Dynamic route params are accessed via `{ params: Promise<Record<string, string>> }`
- Use `next/navigation` for `useRouter`, `useParams`, `usePathname`, `redirect`
- Fonts loaded via `next/font/google` in root layout
- Metadata exported from `layout.tsx` or `page.tsx`
- No `getServerSideProps` or `getStaticProps` -- use Server Components or Route Handlers
- Turbopack enabled for dev (`next dev --turbopack`)
